  "text": "Primary murine chondrocytes (10 6 cells/condition) were treated for 6 h with 50 μM 3-MST inhibitor or 0.4% vehicle (DMSO). They were then resuspended in fluorescenceactivated cell sorting (FACS) buffer (5%FCS, 5 mM EDTA in PBS) and the H 2 S fluorescent probe P3 added (10 μM, [CITATION_1] ). FACS analysis was performed right after with a UV laser (LSRII SORP cytometer, BD Biosciences) and data processed by FACS Diva (BD Biosciences) and FlowJoX (Tree Star).",
